<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Cyrus Byington</author>
<hymn_number>41</hymn_number>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Ʋbanumpa yimmi
 Ai a̱hli fehna ho̱
 Okla e moyuma
 Ish pikbi pullashke.

[C1]
   // Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma! //
   E chim asilhha fehnʋshke.

[V2]
 Okla e moma ka
 Ish pi̱ nukha̱klashke,
 Pi okcha̱ya ta̱kla
 Ish pi yukpalashke:

[C2]
   // Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma! //
   E chim asilhha fehnʋshke.

[V3]
 3 Nitak kanima ho̱
 Ik pihinlo ka wa;
 Pihinla chi̱ bano
 Il ikhaiyanashke:

[C3]
   // Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma! //
   Auet ish pi̱ nukha̱klashke.

[V4]
 4 Haknip ʋt illikma
 Pi shilombish oka
 Chi̱ yakni ʋba ya̱
 Isht ish oyunashke:

[C4]
   // Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma! //
   Ahnit e chim ilbʋshʋshke.

[V5]
 Yʋmma il onakmʋt,
 Nan isht ilaiyukpa
 Ai a̱hli fehna hosh
 Il a̱sha hi oke.

[C5]
   // Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma! //
   Auet ish pim aiahnashke.</lyrics>
<aka>Chisʋs pi̱ Shahli chia ma!</aka>
<time_sig>6.6.6.6.8.8.8.</time_sig>
<title>Prayer to Christ ƲIT41</title>
</song>